Security of information is taken seriously by us; however, remember that no methodology for transmission or data storing is completely safe. Any meaningful transmission of your information has certain inherent risks involved in it. While We support constant development of additional techniques to protect your information, it is hard for Us to guarantee the absolute security of the Internet.

We do not store any of your data on the server in general; your data only goes to your local device and the Google server.
